sources.description:
He loved her and hated her! 
After an enigmatic, self-described pathologist rents the attic room of a Victorian house, his landlady begins to suspect her lodger is Jack the Ripper.

Original title: Man in the Attic (1953)

Colorized version: https://youtu.be/Go4pTx6w1sA

Director: Hugo Fregonese
Writers: Robert Presnell Jr.
Stars: Jack Palance, Constance Smith, Byron Palmer
Genres: Colorized classics, Mystery, Thriller
Budget: $500,000
